		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p><addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee> Editor &#38; Proprietor of &#8220;The Occident.&#8221;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Dear Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">I herewith send you Extracts from several<lb/> Letters recd from <persName>Mr Cresson</persName> from <placeName>Jerusalem</placeName>&#44; which<lb/> I recently spoke to you about &#38; which you kindly offered<lb/> to insert in &#8220;The Occident.&#8221;  <persName>Mr Cresson</persName> is striving<lb/> hard to Establish a school of Agriculture&#44; connecting<add>&#63;</add><lb/> also with the free distribution of Food to our poor co&#45;<lb/>&#61;religionists in <placeName>Jerusalem</placeName> and think from his untiring Energy<lb/> and practical Agricultural knowledge that<lb/> he will succeed in teaching the Israelites<lb/> to become &#8220;practical Farmers.&#8221; provided he is sus&#61;<lb/>&#61;tained with funds for a year or two until it<lb/> becomes firmly established&#44; and a few dollars<lb/> from Each congregation or <del>Judicious</del> wealthy<lb/> Israelite in the <placeName>U. States</placeName> would establish such<lb/> undertaking on a firm basis.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I have received several small<lb/> amounts <del>recently from</del> to forward to him<lb/> as contributions to sustain his Agricultural<lb/> <del>undertaking</del> Establishment &#38; shall <del>make him a rem</del><lb/> <del>&#45;mittance shortly of such amounts as</del> take<lb/> much pleasure in remitting any amounts that<lb/> may be entrusted to my care for that purpose from<lb/> any benevolent Israelites in the <placeName>United States</placeName>.</p>
			<p rend="indent(8)">Yours with respect</p>
			<p rend="indent(9)"><persName role="author">A. Hart</persName></p>
				<p><placeName>Philada</placeName> <date>June 18<hi rend="sup">th</hi> Sivan 22d 5614</date></p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p><addressee>Revd. Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Editor of The Occident</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>371 Walnut St</placeName></p>
		</body>
